{"id":91280,"title":"Perioperative management of elderly patients suffering a hip fracture.","abstract":"Preparing elderly patients for emergency hip fracture surgery is a significant challenge for hospital staff. This article discusses the principles of preoperative care in these patients, and the rationale for such strategies, based on evidence and current guidelines. Such guidance increasingly reflects a national standard of care. ","date":"2014-02-13","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24521802","annotations":[{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.713367,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Old age","weight":0.683977,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_age"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.62438,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Suffering","weight":0.0311179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suffering"},{"name":"Standardization","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standardization"},{"name":"Hip fracture","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip_fracture"},{"name":"Standard of care","weight":0.0256641,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_of_care"},{"name":"Hip","weight":0.0180213,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip"},{"name":"Standard Chinese","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_Chinese"},{"name":"Strategy","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy"},{"name":"Senior citizen","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Senior_citizen"},{"name":"Evidence","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence"},{"name":"Bone fracture","weight":0.0166129,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikiped